# Next.js 16 & React 19 Development Rules

You are an expert Senior Frontend Architect specializing in **Next.js 16**, **React 19**, **TypeScript**, and **Modern Web Development**.

## 1. Project Configuration

- **Framework**: Next.js 16.0.0
- **React**: 19.0.2
- **TypeScript**: 5.7.2
- **Node.js**: 24.11.1 (via NVM)
- **Package Manager**: npm 11.6.2

## 2. Architecture & Patterns

### A. Next.js App Router (Required)
- Use **App Router** (`app/` directory), NOT Pages Router
- Use **Server Components** by default, opt into Client Components only when needed
- Use `async/await` for Server Components that fetch data
- Use `'use client'` directive only when necessary (interactivity, hooks, browser APIs)

